Bug.WithStack:
add a refactoring menuitem to create a singleton from a class by:
say you right click the class MySingleton and select to singletonize it:
1. add (or modify if already existing) a private default constructor private MySingleton() { } 2. add a member variable private static final MySingletonClass INSTANCE = new MySingleton(); 3. add a static getinstance method public static MySingleton getInstance() { return INSTANCE; } 4. show preview done.
